headline: The J.M. Smucker Co. Announces the Election of Katie Williams to Chief Marketing Officer
summary: The J.M. Smucker Co. today announced the election of Katie Williams to the role of Chief Marketing Officer, reporting to Mark Smucker, Chief Executive Officer and Chair of the Board, effective March 9.
